---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<div class="container">
  <div class="text-center mb-5 lg:mb-20 4xl:mb-32">
    <h2 class="section-title font-bold text-white leading-normal">How Trademark Chase Registration Works</h2>
    <p>Get your trademark filed with Trademark Chase in just 3 easy steps</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 xl:px-[8rem] 4xl:px-[1rem] gap-6 lg:gap-10 relative z-[1]">
    <Image 
      src="/assets/img/shap/1.png" 
      alt="shap" 
      width="100" 
      height="100"
      class="object-contain lg:w-full xl:w-[82%] 4xl:w-full h-auto absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 hidden lg:block -z-[1]"
      
    />
    
    <div class="text-center text-white lg:px-7">
      <Image 
        src="/assets/img/icons/1.png" 
        alt="icon" 
        width="50" 
        height="50"
        class="object-contain mx-auto mb-3"
      />
      <h3 class="text-[18px] lg:text-[19px] 4xl:text-[21px] mb-3 font-bold text-white">Conduct a Search</h3>
      <p class="4xl:text-[20px] text-[#ADADAD]">Verify your trademark's uniqueness to avoid conflicts.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="text-center text-white lg:px-7">
      <Image 
        src="/assets/img/icons/2.png" 
        alt="icon" 
        width="50" 
        height="50"
        class="object-contain mx-auto mb-3" 
        
      />
      <h3 class="text-[18px] lg:text-[19px] 4xl:text-[21px] mb-3 font-bold text-white">Submit the Application</h3>
      <p class="4xl:text-[20px] text-[#ADADAD]">File with authorities, specifying your mark and its use.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-white lg:px-7">
      <Image 
        src="/assets/img/icons/3.png" 
        alt="icon" 
        width="50" 
        height="50"
        class="object-contain mx-auto mb-3" 
        
      />
      <h3 class="text-[18px] lg:text-[19px] 4xl:text-[21px] mb-3 font-bold text-white">Examination & Approval</h3>
      <p class="4xl:text-[20px] text-[#ADADAD]">If approved with no objections, your trademark getsÂ registered.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>